Package org.clafer.choco.constraint Description

This package provides Clafer specific Choco constraints required for efficient solving. Most constraints assume that the set envelope and kernel are sorted. The Choco library does not guarantee this to be the case, the compiler needs to guarantee it. The advantage is that some of the propagators can be implemented more efficiently with this guarantee.
